Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.64,0:00:21.45,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找尋著看不見的明天 著急地用手觸摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.60,0:00:25.95,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.10,0:00:38.54,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來是沒有出口的迷宮 就像需要解謎的拼圖一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.20,0:00:49.77,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有奇蹟出現  夢想也將成為勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.94,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.09,0:00:57.86,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.01,0:01:00.40,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  因為那份思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:03.65,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我了無形的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.93,0:01:09.77,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像稍微感受到了迷惘和煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.77,0:01:11.33,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.53,0:01:14.71,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.48,0:01:23.63,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  對你的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.62,0:01:28.59,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.39,0:21:54.70,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在心中綻放的玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.81,0:22:01.54,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中燃盡  僅是一束火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.78,0:22:10.17,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滿是隔閡的街上 如遊戲般的迷失自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.30,0:22:14.42,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小丑的心情躊躇著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.26,0:22:22.76,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要踐踏悲傷的殘片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.92,0:22:27.14,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人在未來中戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.68,0:22:35.24,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以解開今晚的謎底仍然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.52,0:22:39.78,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up！真面目  Hurry up！回到從前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.11,0:22:47.29,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is passion　兩個人的手中充滿的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.41,0:22:54.25,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入黑暗之中  想緊緊擁抱住陽光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.67,0:22:59.80,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在迷宮中相互Kiss
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.96,0:23:08.85,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁向樂園  僅差一道門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.71,0:00:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著時代的演進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.16,0:00:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困難的案件也與日俱增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.06,0:00:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的故事是在雪山山莊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.16,0:00:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被殺的人是不會沉默的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.06,0:00:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.76,0:00:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.06,0:00:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.36,0:00:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.26,0:01:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪山山莊殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.51,0:01:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你不滑雪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.31,0:01:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.41,0:01:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在滑雪之前要好好欣賞這裡的風景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.81,0:01:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片萬里無雲的藍色天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.12,0:01:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.02,0:01:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點綴著銀白色瑞雪的自然景像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.16,0:01:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太壯觀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.63,0:02:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.93,0:02:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就不來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.74,0:02:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把別墅的鑰匙弄丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.80,0:02:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還敢說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是你們做那種事給害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.21,0:02:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我看我們還是打電話給別墅的管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.11,0:02:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他把備份鑰匙帶過來好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這附近又沒有電話亭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.71,0:02:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的出租別墅又還沒有完工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.82,0:02:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑雪專用巴士又已經開走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.92,0:02:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那家私人別墅而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.76,0:02:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會去找在這裡的暴發戶幫我們的忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.43,0:02:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是那種人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.53,0:02:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.43,0:02:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好強行進入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.54,0:02:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不要啦 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.73,0:02:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.36,0:02:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是偵探毛利小五郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.66,0:02:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.96,0:02:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是每次都會在報紙上仔細拜讀的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.61,0:02:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這棟別墅還真是豪華
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就它的設計來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是特別有格調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.42,0:03:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是誰說不想接受這些暴發戶的幫忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.12,0:03:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.32,0:03:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有請教這位小姐芳名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.13,0:03:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就是毛利先生的千金 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.43,0:03:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我是小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子是江戶川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.53,0:03:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的一個朋友寄放在我們家的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.40,0:03:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個把手採用獅子的造型真是太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.11,0:03:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是馬就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.31,0:03:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來好像沒那麼順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.46,0:03:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.76,0:03:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.36,0:03:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜歡獅子喜歡馬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.12,0:03:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我指的不是這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.62,0:03:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.76,0:03:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是中原啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼那麼慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.63,0:03:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都已經在等你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.73,0:03:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.06,0:03:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是我剛才偶然碰到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.63,0:03:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.50,0:03:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你們都是同一所醫科大學的醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.46,0:03:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在聚在這裡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.51,0:03:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是大山教授的學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.21,0:04:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實做醫生也是有門派之分的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.36,0:04:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經在大山教授手下跟著他學了幾十年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.42,0:04:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於我是在三年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.12,0:04:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一個一直默默無聞的教授那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.66,0:04:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉到大山教授手下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.03,0:04:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初這個決定做得實在是太正確了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.43,0:04:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天大山教授發表的那篇論文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.03,0:04:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可謂是學術巨作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.33,0:04:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得是一篇探討有關大腸癌遺傳因子的治療開發的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在系上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.21,0:04:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都對教授的論文讚不絕口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.81,0:04:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼 我這顆不平凡的腦袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.86,0:04:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫出那種論文有什麼難的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.12,0:04:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.32,0:04:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記買下酒菜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.62,0:04:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就到山底下那家便利商店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.23,0:04:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買一些上來好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.43,0:04:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便幫我買包洋芋片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.03,0:04:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要魷魚乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要生菜沙拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.33,0:04:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們通通寫在紙上吧 我都幫你們買回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.53,0:04:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.61,0:05:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家便利商店十點鐘就會關門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.16,0:05:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你動作可要快點哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.01,0:05:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.81,0:05:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在幾點鐘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八點五十八分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.86,0:05:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.62,0:05:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.72,0:05:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跑去看電視了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.52,0:05:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正著迷於目前九點檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.76,0:05:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收視率達百分之三十的那個愛情連續劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.46,0:05:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個我也有在看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.53,0:05:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛田醫生 你要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.03,0:05:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去滑夜雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.90,0:05:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上滑得不過癮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在十一點之前回到這裡來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.01,0:05:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下酒菜來之前 我就到澡堂裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.72,0:05:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡個舒服的澡好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.76,0:05:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把別墅鑰匙弄丟的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.52,0:05:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話告訴管理員了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.42,0:05:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事情我早就忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.03,0:05:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.53,0:05:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們今天就住在這裡好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.23,0:06:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看妳爸爸醉成那個樣子也回不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.20,0:06:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把這包垃圾拿到外面去倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.31,0:06:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等 小勉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要離開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.32,0:06:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣子 光江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.92,0:06:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個人絕對不可以在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我求求妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.52,0:06:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求妳對我死心好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.82,0:06:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.63,0:06:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們兩個不能在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.16,0:06:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳回來了 香織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.23,0:06:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外頭雪這麼大 車子很難開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.34,0:06:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛田醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.26,0:06:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我滑到一半突然下起大雪來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒辦法滑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.65,0:06:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.25,0:06:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在喝啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.75,0:06:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡個澡覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.96,0:06:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請妳買的生菜沙拉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.46,0:07:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起 已經賣光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.26,0:07:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且冰淇淋也已經沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.06,0:07:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰在這麼冷的天氣要我買冰淇淋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.33,0:07:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是大山教授吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.33,0:07:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那個人是最愛吃冰淇淋的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.14,0:07:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.84,0:07:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個連續劇十點鐘就應該結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.24,0:07:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯伯怎麼還沒有下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.04,0:07:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山教授每次都會把那個節目錄下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.84,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好看的鏡頭他會看好幾次呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.75,0:07:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.15,0:07:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來他一開始就打這個主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.96,0:07:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才把我約來別墅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.36,0:07:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你的詭計得逞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.56,0:07:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有那個名偵探毛利小五郎在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.53,0:07:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定會發現我留下的這個訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.84,0:07:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是常在報紙上出現的那個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.64,0:07:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸是個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.54,0:07:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經過十一點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.75,0:07:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不覺得那個伯伯太慢了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.46,0:08:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去那邊看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是那個名人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.26,0:08:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是人不可貌相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.96,0:08:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山教授
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.24,0:08:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.96,0:08:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經斷氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.14,0:08:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先把繩子解開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.05,0:08:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西都不准碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.35,0:08:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼可以擅自破壞一個兇殺現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.95,0:08:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.75,0:08:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方跟救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.26,0:08:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為外頭雪下得太大了 不可能上山來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.26,0:08:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.66,0:08:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.46,0:08:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又輪到我名偵探毛利小五郎出場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒還沒醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了謹慎起見 我再問一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.04,0:08:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們剛才沒有人碰過這屋裡的東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.14,0:08:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.04,0:09:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了大山教授的遺體之外其他的都沒碰過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現屍體的人是中原小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.85,0:09:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也沒有碰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.35,0:09:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到教授全身都是血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.95,0:09:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一進門的時候就被嚇得全身發軟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.35,0:09:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間裡面有沒有擺什麼值錢的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.66,0:09:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得教授的保險箱就放在電視機右邊的櫃子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.66,0:09:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面都是刮痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.93,0:09:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道這裡面裝了什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.04,0:09:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 裝的應該都是現金吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.34,0:09:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為教授向來喜歡把鉅款帶在身上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.66,0:09:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說兇手的目的是錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.15,0:09:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些血跡是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.35,0:09:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是努力往牆壁爬去的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.95,0:09:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這個人怎麼會跪坐著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.86,0:09:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桌上的血跡剛好形成一條整齊的直線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.36,0:09:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 上面原來放著桌布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.73,0:09:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是沾血繩子的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.93,0:09:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.23,0:10:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是大山先生的死前訊息嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.84,0:10:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手在玻璃上貼上膠布後打破玻璃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.86,0:10:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再闖入到屋子裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.05,0:10:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶外面果然還有兇手到這裡的足跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一下子我大概知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.56,0:10:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嗯什麼嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我到那邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.46,0:10:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.56,0:10:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在能不能請你們來驗屍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.03,0:10:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其讓我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是讓你們幾位醫生來做會更適合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.53,0:10:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.66,0:10:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.34,0:10:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山教授他最引以為豪的這隻金錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.74,0:10:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沾滿了血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正經一點行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.56,0:10:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這個時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.25,0:10:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我推斷正確的死亡時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.65,0:10:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是下午九點半到十點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.95,0:10:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.15,0:10:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是大山先生在房間裡面看那部連續劇的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.86,0:10:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.66,0:10:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的身上雖然有許多的傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.96,0:10:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最直接的死因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.43,0:11:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為應該是這兩道貫穿肺部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引起刺傷後的窒息才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.73,0:11:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺傷後窒息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為肺部穿孔的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.24,0:11:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被害人想要呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.46,0:11:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肺部也無法擴張了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒法呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.74,0:11:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 大山教授被刺的十到十五分鐘之內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.74,0:11:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是非常痛苦才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.05,0:11:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底誰會做這種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.35,0:11:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我推測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.55,0:11:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行兇的動機應該就是錢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.95,0:11:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手從窗戶進來以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.36,0:11:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把當時正在看電視的大山教授先綁了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.86,0:11:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就逼問他保險箱的號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.66,0:11:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他沒有說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候兇手一生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.13,0:11:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用刀刺向大山教授
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.53,0:11:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後又從窗戶這裡逃出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.54,0:11:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.24,0:11:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看這個伯伯的錶是金子做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.04,0:11:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個伯伯不是被綁起來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個跑進來的強盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.35,0:11:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然沒有搶他的金錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真幸運耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.75,0:11:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手的目的既然是錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.56,0:12:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會留下那金錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這個兇手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.93,0:12:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個兇手還真是粗心大意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.53,0:12:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你們不認為這個兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.03,0:12:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽子挺大的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.04,0:12:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看窗戶外面的腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.04,0:12:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個兇手根本毫不考慮就直接走到這個房間來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.25,0:12:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.85,0:12:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的話 心裡一定會害怕房間裡有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.45,0:12:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以會在窗戶外面偷看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.35,0:12:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到確定屋子的情況之後才進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.46,0:12:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.26,0:12:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 難道會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.36,0:12:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保險箱外面有那麼多刮痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.43,0:12:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及大山教授會被綁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.83,0:12:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只是這個兇手所刻意要給外人看的假像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.24,0:12:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實兇手他早就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.24,0:12:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候大山教授他會一個人在這裡看電視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也就是說兇手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.25,0:12:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你們這四個人當中的其中一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.25,0:12:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.95,0:13:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.75,0:13:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就讓我來一個一個問你們好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.35,0:13:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們從九點半到十點之間的不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我到便利商店去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.76,0:13:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我離開的時候是九點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.83,0:13:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來的時候已經是九點五十分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.73,0:13:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出門前大家拜託我買回來的小菜和點心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.63,0:13:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以沒有買齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.24,0:13:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為生菜沙拉跟冰淇淋都已經賣完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.64,0:13:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果開快一點應該可以更早到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.54,0:13:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往返的時間至少就要花四十分鐘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.34,0:13:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不相信的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以開我的車子去試試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時出去滑夜雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.85,0:13:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往返滑雪場同樣也要花四十分鐘的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.95,0:13:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有證據嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.55,0:13:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.56,0:13:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張夜間滑雪門票上還印了今天的日期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.16,0:13:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連時間也打上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.13,0:13:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我跟小蘭還有柯南三個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.23,0:13:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都留在這兒整理東西跟洗碗和盤子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.93,0:13:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江角小姐只有出去倒垃圾而離開了兩、三分鐘而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.74,0:13:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從九點到十點之間都在澡堂裡泡澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.34,0:14:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在場證明最不明確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了金澤先生之外還有一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.96,0:14:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血…血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.75,0:14:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙發上怎麼會沒有血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.56,0:14:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是血乾了之後被什麼人放到這兒的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.16,0:14:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張桌布上面也都是血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.63,0:14:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.53,0:14:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全吻合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.63,0:14:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個打火機原本是放在這兒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.34,0:14:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.74,0:14:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.84,0:14:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山教授白天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.94,0:14:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是馬就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來好像沒那麼順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.25,0:14:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得這的確是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.05,0:14:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟小蘭向大山教授自我介紹時說的名字...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.15,0:14:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來他說的馬指的是這個意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.85,0:14:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是大山教授留下的死亡訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.56,0:14:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他之所以會跪坐在地板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.56,0:14:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有血乾了的打火機被放在沙發上的謎題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都可以解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.63,0:14:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那個兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.23,0:14:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像留下的死亡訊息裡所說的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的 一定就是那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.06,0:15:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.76,0:15:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙發上有個好奇怪的東西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.46,0:15:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有完沒完 可惡的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.96,0:15:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.26,0:15:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔好像喝酒喝醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 我才沒有喝醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的事情我都明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.04,0:15:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.74,0:15:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.24,0:15:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死大山教授的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.05,0:15:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經知道是什麼人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.35,0:15:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先就是晚上出去滑夜雪的飛田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他絕對不可能信口胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.16,0:15:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這件事只要一查就會知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.26,0:15:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著是江角小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.16,0:15:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發時 她只離開小蘭跟柯南兩、三分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.26,0:15:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在這段時間裡殺死大山教授那是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.67,0:15:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 沒有不在場證明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.87,0:15:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩下金澤先生還有中原小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.94,0:15:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.34,0:15:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過我下山去幫大家買下酒的小菜了嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.34,0:16:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 全部一共是多少錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.34,0:16:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情我早就已經忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.46,0:16:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.35,0:16:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.55,0:16:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是妳不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.05,0:16:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為妳早就在白天上山的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.55,0:16:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就事先把很多種類的小菜買好了存起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確切地說是在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.56,0:16:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳白天下山買火鍋材料的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.36,0:16:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在行兇之前先問大家要買的東西之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.56,0:16:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動車子只是裝裝樣子而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.87,0:16:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.87,0:16:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳找了一個地方把車子停好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.74,0:16:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再從車子裡把他們託妳買的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.56,0:16:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從袋子裡挑出來就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.96,0:16:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來妳就有不在場證明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.06,0:16:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以趁那個時候將大山教授殺死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.95,0:16:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就沒有證據 不要信口胡說行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.05,0:16:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想妳也應該知道才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.95,0:16:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.25,0:16:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就清楚地留有妳就是兇手的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.76,0:16:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看看桌子上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血跡被清楚地切斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.86,0:16:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想 上面原來有什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.36,0:16:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那張桌布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.77,0:16:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請你們以讓血跡吻合的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.56,0:17:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這張桌布放到桌子上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.84,0:17:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是大山教授所留下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.44,0:17:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗示兇手是誰的死亡訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個死亡訊息要怎麼看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.35,0:17:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們仔細想想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.45,0:17:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山教授他是跪坐在地上死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.55,0:17:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你們應該就可以知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.26,0:17:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們五人的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.46,0:17:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山教授用將棋都暗示出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將棋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.46,0:17:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.47,0:17:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山教授平常就常掛在嘴邊說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.57,0:17:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有馬就萬事俱備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.74,0:17:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.34,0:17:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了那馬以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.46,0:17:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的棋子都在這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.04,0:17:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.04,0:17:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳把沙發上的那個打火機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.84,0:17:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放到這張桌布上面看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.85,0:17:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.15,0:17:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個打火機上的血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.76,0:17:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟桌布上能夠吻合的地方也只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.25,0:17:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.56,0:17:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是香車的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.56,0:17:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.66,0:18:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是香車初始的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.86,0:18:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中原香織小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.97,0:18:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這棋就是大山教授暗示兇手就是妳所留下來的死亡訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.54,0:18:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在桌布放上去之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.74,0:18:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道桌布擺的正不正確呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.24,0:18:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們再仔細看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.34,0:18:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整張桌子上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.54,0:18:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有打火機那個地方的血流得最長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.55,0:18:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說那裡就是桌子最靠近邊緣的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.25,0:18:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這一切只是一個巧合罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.06,0:18:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.16,0:18:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳為什麼要把那張桌布移走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.16,0:18:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妳把桌布移開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.56,0:18:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那一定是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.56,0:18:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跟大山教授糾纏的時候才會弄掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.47,0:18:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.84,0:18:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桌布邊緣的血跡很清晰地沾在桌子上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.94,0:18:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沾滿血跡的打火機雖然放在沙發上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙發上卻沒有沾上任何的血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.34,0:18:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是血跡乾了以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.55,0:18:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被什麼人移動過的最有力的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.35,0:18:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.75,0:19:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是兇手後來再度回到兇案現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.46,0:19:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她發現了這個資訊後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.36,0:19:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所能夠想到唯一的掩飾方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.06,0:19:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是這樣 中原香織小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香織...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.57,0:19:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的運氣實在差了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.13,0:19:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳發現這個死亡訊息的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.14,0:19:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在妳發出了尖叫之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.24,0:19:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外還有一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.94,0:19:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳對大家說便利商店裡的生菜沙拉還有冰淇淋都賣光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生菜沙拉還有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.55,0:19:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋是不可能賣光的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.96,0:19:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.15,0:19:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山教授的確是我殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.65,0:19:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳為什麼要殺教授
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.56,0:19:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們之間的感情不是一直都很好的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.96,0:19:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.06,0:19:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直把他當成自己的父親看待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.86,0:19:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這樣 我才不能夠原諒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.36,0:19:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他竟然把我寫的論文拿去占為己有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.57,0:19:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說就是那一篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.24,0:19:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腸癌遺傳因子的治療開發的論文嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.04,0:19:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.54,0:19:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他從我這裡搶走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.34,0:19:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在過去這六年裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.04,0:19:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耗費了我所有的心血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.44,0:19:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易完成那篇論文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.85,0:20:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那篇是為我死去的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.46,0:20:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別寫的論文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.16,0:20:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.06,0:20:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我很小的時候就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他死於大腸癌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.96,0:20:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會成為一個醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.66,0:20:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會專心致力於大腸癌方面的研究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.06,0:20:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了救像我父親一樣的病人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.07,0:20:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我沒有想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.23,0:20:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易寫成的論文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.06,0:20:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被別人搶走了 而且是被他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.64,0:20:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.04,0:20:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今妳再對別人說那是妳的論文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會有人相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.45,0:20:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.45,0:20:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我這個教授來發妳你的論文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.25,0:20:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才可能受到世人矚目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.45,0:20:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你死去的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.05,0:20:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會更高興才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想到了這一次的殺人計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.86,0:20:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對我父親的思念完全被這個人給踐踏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.16,0:20:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就想到將他的肺部開一個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.16,0:20:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這種最痛苦的方式來把他解決掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.24,0:20:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我沒有想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.24,0:20:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在這麼痛苦的十幾分鐘之內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.24,0:21:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能夠留下這些死亡訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.26,0:21:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗示我就是殺他的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.84,0:21:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過名偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.45,0:21:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的這番推理有一個地方說錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.25,0:21:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實冰淇淋跟生菜沙拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.45,0:21:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就想到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.15,0:21:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙拉當時的確已經被賣光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.16,0:21:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是冰淇淋我的確有買回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.16,0:21:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.76,0:21:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在車子裡面完全融掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.16,0:21:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把大家要的東西包成一袋放在前座上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.17,0:21:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我就要開始行動的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.83,0:21:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻突然想起了我死去的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.34,0:21:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那短短的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.34,0:21:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就被暖氣給融化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.14,0:21:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.24,0:21:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他託我買的冰淇淋竟然揭穿了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.45,0:21:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.56,0:21:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.23,0:23:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.64,0:23:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在有些案例之中都會以出人意料的方式表現出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.65,0:23:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拐你的腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.85,0:23:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下看你要怎麼樣扭轉這個劣勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.16,0:23:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.55,0:23:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.36,0:23:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時就算再平常的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.56,0:23:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(奇怪 你怎麼還沒有被拐死啊)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.96,0:23:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要轉換一下視角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.96,0:23:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(你再往上面看一點點)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.93,0:23:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(バカ)笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.53,0:23:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.24,0:23:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在游泳池死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.04,0:23:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是溺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.15,0:23:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.25,0:23:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是所有死在水裡面的人都是被溺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.05,0:23:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幅畫難道是你從這邊看出去畫的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.05,0:24:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.96,0:24:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.66,0:24:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手就是那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.26,0:24:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.16,0:24:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這的確是一宗看似意外的殺人案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.26,0:24:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.46,0:24:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體育俱樂部殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.16,0:24:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.66,0:24:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.76,0:24:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集是很流行的體育俱樂部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.76,0:24:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 元太又要再跑了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.46,0:24:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
